e_ai_management_tool_springaiconfigexporter", "label": "SpringAiConfigExporter.java (proposed)", "file_type": "code", "source_file": "docs/claude_ai_management_tool.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "The Spring AI config exporter is framed as the feature that makes Port Wrangler genuinely useful beyond running containers \u2014 once a model is running, developers get a one-click copy of the exact Spring AI config needed to use it in their own app, delivering 'easy integration management' as the core value proposition."}, {"id": "docs_claude_ai_management_tool_ai_api_endpoints", "label": "/api/ai/* REST endpoints (proposed)", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/claude_ai_management_tool.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "docs_claude_ai_management_tool_aimodelspage_jsx", "label": "AiModelsPage.jsx (proposed frontend)", "file_type": "code", "source_file": "docs/claude_ai_management_tool.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "docs_claude_ai_management_tool_deploypage_jsx", "label": "DeployPage.jsx (referenced layout pattern)", "file_type": "code", "source_file": "docs/claude_ai_management_tool.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "docs_claude_ai_management_tool_ollama_managed_container_decision", "label": "Ollama as managed container vs. pre-existing (design decision)", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "docs/claude_ai_management_tool.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Could treat Ollama exactly like PostgreSQL (deploy via Port Wrangler, fully managed) or assume users have Ollama installed natively and point Spring AI at localhost:11434; the managed-container approach fits the existing UX better and makes the tool fully self-contained."}, {"id": "docs_claude_ai_management_tool_model_pull_async_pipeline", "label": "Model pull as async pipeline (design decision)", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "docs/claude_ai_management_tool.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Model pulls can take minutes for large models (70B is ~40GB); reusing the existing PipelineOrchestrator and SSE polling gives progress tracking for free instead of inventing a new mechanism."}], "edges": [{"source": "docs_claude_ai_management_tool_pipelineorchestrator", "target": "docs_claude_ai_management_tool_ollamaapiclient", "relation": "references", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "docs/claude_ai_management_tool.md", "source_location": null, "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "docs_claude_ai_management_tool_pipelineorchestrator", "target": "docs_claude_ai_management_tool_dockerdeployengine", "relation": "shares_data_with", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "docs/claude_ai_management_tool.md", "source_location": null, "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "docs_claude_ai_management_tool_aimodelcatalog", "target": "docs_claude_ai_management_tool_databasecatalog", "relation": "conceptually_related_to", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "docs/claude_ai_management_tool.md", "source_location": null, "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "docs_claude_ai_management_tool_ollamaapiclient", "target": "docs_claude_ai_management_tool_aimodelinstance", "relation": "shares_data_with", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "docs/claude_ai_management_tool.md", "source_location": null, "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "docs_claude_ai_management_tool_springaiconfigexporter", "target": "docs_claude_ai_management_tool_ai_api_endpoints", "relation": "shares_data_with", "confidence": "E